        "---\n",
        "title: Is identification possible for machines ?\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Methods\n",
        "### Features\n",
        "- Long-Term Average Spectra (LTAS)\n",
        "- Long-Term Cepstral Coefficients (LTCC)\n",
        "- Long-Term Mel-Frequency Cepstral Coefficients (LTMFCC)\n",
        "\n",
        "### Classifiers\n",
        "- K-Nearest Neighbors (KNN)\n",
        "- Support Vector Machines (SVM)\n",
        "- Multi-Layer Perceptron (MLP)\n",
        "\n",
        "## Results"
      ],
      "id": "e4f8a84b"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
